<DOC><DOCNO>WSJ900622-0158</DOCNO><DOCID>900622-0158.</DOCID><HL>   Italian Wholesale Sales Index</HL><DATE>06/22/90</DATE><SO>WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C6</SO><CO>   EUROP</CO><LP>   MILAN -- Italy's industrial wholesale sales index in Marchrose 5.7% from a year earlier, the state statisticalinstitute Istat said.   In February, the index rose 5.3% from a year earlier.Domestic wholesale sales in March rose 5.3%, and sales toforeign destinations grew 6.7%.</LP><TEXT>   For the first three months of this year, wholesale salesrose 5.9% from the year-earlier period, owing to increases of5.2% in domestic sales and 8% in foreign sales.   Sales of capital products to both foreign and domesticdestinations in the first three months grew 10.4% from a yearearlier, and wholesale sales of consumer products rose 8.3%.Sales of intermediate goods rose 0.9%.</TEXT></DOC>